apps/web — Next.js 14 (App Router), TypeScript strict, Tailwind, Geist via geist/font/sans, rewrites in next.config.mjs (Next 14 doesn’t load next.config.ts) so /api/v1/* is proxied to NEXT_PUBLIC_API_URL (default http://127.0.0.1:8787). Placeholder routes match your list.
